   "source": [
    "# DSE4211 Group 18 — Cryptocurrency Bubble Prediction\n",
    "## End-to-End Rolling-Window Evaluation\n",
    "\n",
    "**Rolling scheme**: 9-month train → 3-month validation (hyper-parameter tuning) → 3-month test, advancing 3 months per fold.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Models**: LASSO · XGBoost, each trained as a *per-coin* model and as a single *global* model.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Class imbalance**:\n",
    "- LASSO — `class_weight='balanced'` (same as `lasso.ipynb`) + SMOTE applied to the training fold.\n",
    "- XGBoost — SMOTE applied to the training fold (same as `xgboost.ipynb`)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 0 · Imports & Setup"
